WEBVTT

00:23:20.357 --> 00:23:24.945 line:95%,end
LISA

00:23:25.028 --> 00:23:26.405 line:95%,end
<i>BLACKPINK THE MOVIE</i>

00:23:26.488 --> 00:23:28.740 line:95%,end
<i>It was the most fun I had in my life.</i>

00:23:28.824 --> 00:23:29.658 line:95%,end
A LISA FILM

00:23:29.741 --> 00:23:31.701 line:95%,end
<i>And I had the best time of my life.</i>

00:23:32.953 --> 00:23:35.956 line:95%,end
<i>Like for the rest of my life,
I think I’ll continue to remember</i>

00:23:36.915 --> 00:23:38.875 line:95%,end
<i>that moment, that feeling.</i>

00:23:41.086 --> 00:23:44.297 line:95%,end
<i>A lot of things happened.
There were happy times,</i>

00:23:44.381 --> 00:23:46.383 line:95%,end
<i>and there were sad times.</i>

00:23:46.466 --> 00:23:49.219 line:95%,end
<i>I think those were the happiest times.</i>

00:24:00.772 --> 00:24:03.442 line:95%,end
<i>Oddly, when I try
to recollect difficult times,</i>

00:24:03.525 --> 00:24:06.695 line:95%,end
<i>I can’t seem to remember them.</i>

00:24:07.571 --> 00:24:12.367 line:95%,end
<i>I just erase everything
that has to do with difficult times</i>

00:24:12.451 --> 00:24:13.994 line:95%,end
<i>from my mind without realizing it.</i>

00:24:14.077 --> 00:24:17.247 line:95%,end
<i>I don’t think
I’m overly positive or outgoing.</i>

00:24:17.330 --> 00:24:19.583 line:95%,end
<i>I am a normal person
just like everyone else.</i>

00:24:19.666 --> 00:24:23.295 line:95%,end
<i>Every day I’m like this.
I’m like this every day.</i>

00:24:33.305 --> 00:24:38.351 line:95%,end
<i>I knew what I wanted to do
since I was young.</i>

00:24:38.435 --> 00:24:42.022 line:95%,end
<i>I believe I am a very lucky person.</i>

00:24:42.564 --> 00:24:46.276 line:95%,end
<i>I had a clear goal
to become a superstar in the future.</i>

00:24:46.359 --> 00:24:49.613 line:95%,end
<i>I worked hard to make my dream come true.</i>

00:25:00.999 --> 00:25:03.502 line:95%,end
<i>I try to think that I am happy,</i>

00:25:04.211 --> 00:25:08.507 line:95%,end
<i>without having to stress out too much.</i>

00:25:08.590 --> 00:25:12.928 line:95%,end
<i>I hope others could also think like that.</i>

00:25:14.846 --> 00:25:16.264 line:95%,end
<i>Life is super short.</i>

